data.description: Welcome to your new home!  This unique 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence offers the best of all worlds: space, tranquility and convenience. Nestled on a spacious lot adorned with mature trees and a captivating water feature, this location can't be beaten. Located close to town, you'll enjoy the convenience of being within walking distance to downtown Louisville, with its vibrant shops and eclectic restaurants,  as well as top rated BVSD schools and all of the nearby trails to explore the great outdoors. This home offers many functional spaces. The open concept kitchen, featuring a generous island and convenient breakfast bar flows seamlessly into the dining area and family room, creating a welcoming atmosphere, ideal for entertaining guests or simply enjoying quality time with loved ones. Boasting 5 bedrooms, plus an office, there is ample space for everyone. Move in as is or consider creating a huge primarily suite while still retaining 3 additional bedrooms and an office. Outside, the large yard, lush landscaping, ample privacy and the sound of running water combine to create a unique and special oasis. Don't miss this home with numerous bedrooms, located on a huge lot, in an ideal location in Louisville all for under $1M! This home presents an incredible opportunity for those seeking a unique property with unlimited potential.
